headline: Revvity (RVTY) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: Revvity (RVTY) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +4.29% and +0.02%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
